item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】MP3 - Silent Hill: Otherworld Echoes (Vol. 1) [2023]
item.description:
Silent Hill: Otherworld Echoes (Vol. 1) is the first compilation of covers of the Silent Hill soundtracks, originally performed by Akira Yamaoka, Daniel Licht, Mary Elizabeth McGlynn and Joe Romersa. These songs were masterfully covered by talented singers and rock bands who honored the video game franchise with their music. Thank you so much, the credit is all yours. You deserved so much recognition for this and hell of subscribers. That's why I'm inviting you to subscribe to their YouTube channels and other platforms so that you can enjoy their amazing musical performances. The playlist cover was designed by https://vk.com/dan.mason.

1. Silent Hill - Mark Lambert
2. Waiting For You - GaMetal Feat. Lacey Johnson
